- id
- name
- email (unique)
- password
- role (enum: 'admin', 'superadmin') default: 'admin'
- timestamps

### 2. services

- id
- title_ar (string)
- icon (string - URL or path)
- short_description_ar (text)
- long_description_ar (text)
- points (json - array of strings)
- image (string - URL or path)
- sort_order (integer, default 0)
- is_active (boolean, default true)
- timestamps

### 3. contacts

- id
- type (enum: 'contact', 'social')
- title (string)
- icon (string)
- value (string)
- link (string)
- sort_order (integer, default 0)
- is_active (boolean, default true)
- timestamps

### 4. settings

- id
- key (string, unique)
- value (text)
- timestamps

Seed settings table with:

- key: 'consultation_email', value: 'admin@example.com'

### 5. consultations

- id
- name (string)
- phone (string)
- email (string)
- service_id (foreign key -> services.id, nullable)
- message (text, nullable)
- is_read (boolean, default false)
- timestamps

