## ADMIN DASHBOARD (web routes, prefix: /admin)

### Authentication

- /admin/login - Login page (email + password form)
- /admin/logout - POST logout
- Protect all /admin/\* routes with auth middleware
- After login redirect to /admin/dashboard
- Default seeded admin: email: admin@admin.com, password: password

### Dashboard Home (/admin/dashboard)

- Stats cards: total services, total contacts, total socials, total consultations (unread count highlighted)

### Services Management (/admin/services)

- Index: table listing all services with sort_order, is_active toggle, edit/delete buttons, "Add New" button
- Create: form with all fields (title_ar, icon URL input, short_description_ar, long_description_ar, points (dynamic add/remove rows with JS), image URL input, sort_order, is_active)
- Edit: same form pre-filled
- Delete: with confirmation
- points field should be a dynamic list: user can click "Add Point" to add a new text input row and remove any row

### Contacts Management (/admin/contacts)

- Index: table showing all contacts and socials, separated by type, with edit/delete/add buttons
- Create: form with fields (type dropdown: contact or social, title, icon URL, value, link, sort_order, is_active)
- Edit: same form pre-filled
- Delete: with confirmation

### Consultations (/admin/consultations)

- Index: table showing all consultations (name, phone, email, service name, message truncated, date, read status)
- Show: detail view of a single consultation, mark as read automatically when opened
- Delete: with confirmation
- Filter by: read/unread

### Settings (/admin/settings)

- Single page form with:
  1. Consultation Email (the email address to receive consultation notifications) - input type email
  2. Site Name - text input
- Save button updates the settings table

### User Management (/admin/users)

- Index: table of all admin users with name, email, role, edit/delete buttons, "Add New" button
- Create: form (name, email, password, password_confirmation, role)
- Edit: form (name, email, role, optional new password)
- Delete: cannot delete own account
- Roles: admin, superadmin

